Download TIGER shapes for Combined Statistical Area

Source: R/csa.R
tt_csa.Rd

Download TIGER shapes for Combined Statistical Area

Usage

tt_csa(year = 2021)

Arguments

year

Integer year. Required. 2000 and 2010-2024 are currently supported.

Value

sf data.frame

Examples

# Wrapped in try due to false positive 304 errors
try(tt_csa())
